                },
                {
                  "nickName": "Guest User",
                  "regionCode": "",
                  "content": "Loved, loved the close proximity to transport via tube or bus and almost anything else you could want or need in food and/or entertainment. However, we could not sleep at night as there was constant yelling and cussing of people all night long. We were on the fifth floor and it felt like the people were sharing our room, they  were so loud! The hotel could also use some blackout shades or curtains, that is more a personal preference. Staff were wonderful!",
