                  "nickName": "Guest User",
                  "regionCode": "",
                  "content": "We had room 1004 and the view was fantastic.  EVERY member of staff we encountered were very friendly, helpful and courteous - for me this goes a long way, even if the facilities are not good, which they definitely were here.   The hotel is spotlessly clean, the room has every convenience you need and the breakfast was so vast in choice, not to mention that the coffee was superb!  We had intended to go into town for a meal before our concert, but as it was raining and there was also a football match on that night, we ate at the hotel and was pleasantly surprised at the quality (was expecting the usual fast food burgers or pizza).  Definitely will return next time we go to Manchester.",
