              "lat": 31.23462065011125,
              "lon": 121.47326981809898,
              "brief": "The Radisson Blu Hotel Shanghai New World is located on Nanjing Road in the commercial hub and premium shopping area of Shanghai. The hotel is situated opposite the People\u2019s Park and right above the People\u2019s Square subway station with easy access to Metro Lines 1, 2 and 8. &#60;br&#62;&#60;br&#62;Tempt your taste buds with flavors from around the world at any of the five dining outlets. See the city like never before from your seat at Epicure on 45, our revolving restaurants stunning Shanghai views. Sample a little of everything from the international buffets at Windows on the Park. In the evening enjoy live music and innovative at Sky Dome Bar. &#60;br&#62;&#60;br&#62;With 1018 square meters of meeting space, eleven different rooms and easy metro access, the hotel is an ideal choice for important events.&#60;br&#62;&#60;br&#62;Treat yourself to a revitalizing massage in the on-site spa, or swim a few laps in the modern indoor heated pool and Wifi covering the hotel. &#60;br&#62;&#60;br&#62;The hotel is adjacent to the famous New World City shopping center, which is directly accessible from the hotel lobby, including a large shopping mall, Madame Tussauds, Naruto World, Cinema, Universe Climbing GYM and Snow1, etc., with unparalleled convenience.",
